title: Champion of aDrive
name: Gnawbie - Champion of aDrive
printed_effect:
When you Cast this Gnawbie you can Search
your deck for an aDrive and add it to your hand.
You can Nexus {lunar}.
{wind} card that receives {lunar} this way is Unaffected
by Counter Runes until the next turn.
